d win.} 16. d5 c4 17. Nd4 {[%eval -167,22]} (17. b4 $1 $11 {[%eval -21,18]}) 17... N7e5 {[%eval -97,17]} (17... cxb3 $19 {[%eval -167,22] Strongly threatening ...Be7-c5.} 18. Ncb5 (18. dxe6 $2 N7c5 $19 {[%csl Od4][%mdl 64] Discovered Attack}) (18. Nc6 $2 Rxc6 19. dxc6 N7e5 $19) 18... Nxf2 19. Kxf2 Bc5) 18. b4 $17 {Dodges Be7-c5} axb4 19. axb4 Nxb4 20. Nce2 {[%eval -102,19] [#]} (20. Qh5 $1 $15 {[%eval -64,20] might be stronger.} Ned3 21. Na2) 20... Bb7 $1 (20... exd5 21. Bxb4 Bxb4 22. exd5 $16 (22. Rxa6 Ng4 $16)) 21. dxe6 Nbd3 22. Ra7 Rc7 23. exf7+ Rxf7 24. Ne6 {[%eval -200,21]} (24. f4 $17 {[%eval -123,20]} Ng4 25. Ne6) 24... Qb8 $19 25. Nxc7 {Hoping for Ra7xb7!} Qxa7 26. Nf4 Bc5 27. Nce6 Bxe3 28. Bxe3 h6 {Against Ne6-g5} 29. h3 Qa8 30. Nd5 Qa5 31. f4 Nd7 32. Bd2 {[%eval -229,21]} (32. Nd8 $17 {[%eval -131,19]} Bxd5 33. exd5) 32... Qa2 33. Nc3 {[#]} Qb2 {[%eval 0,24]} (33... Qa8 $1 $19 {[%eval -180,20] Threatens to win with ...Nd7-f6.} 34. Qb1 N3c5) 34. Nd8 $36 {White is pushing.} Nf6 35. Nxf7 Kxf7 36. e5 Bxg2 37. exf6 Bc6 (37... Bxh3 $2 38. Qh5+ Kxf6 (38... g6 $2 39. Qxh3 Qa1+ 40. Kh2 $18) 39. Qe8 $18 (39. Qxh3 Kg6 $18) (39. Qxh3 Kg6 $18)) 38. fxg7 Kg8 39. Qe2 Qa1+ 40. Nd1 $1 Qd4+ (40... Kxg7 $2 41. Bc3+ $18) 41. Kf1 $2 {[%eval -1122,28]} (41. Kh2 $11 {[%eval 0,21]} Qd5 (41... Qxg7 $2 {loses.} 42. Qe6+ Qf7 43. Qxc6 $18) 42. g4) 41... Qd5 $1 {Weighted Error Value: White=0.33/Black=0.18 (very precise)} (41... Qxg7 $2 {is the wrong capture.} 42. Qe6+ Kh7 43. Qxc6 $18) (41... Kxg7 $2 {perishes.} 42. Bc3 {[%mdl 64] Pin} Kf7 43. Bxd4 $18) 0-1


