1 {[%eval 7,19] should be considered.} 21. Qa2 (21. Qxb5 Rb8 $17) 21... Qd7) 21. Qf3 $14 c4 {[%eval 66,20]} (21... Rc8 $11 {[%eval 21,17]}) 22. e4 $1 dxe4 {[%eval 105,19]} (22... Rb8 $14 {[%eval 67,21]} 23. Be5 dxe4 24. Nxe4 Rc8) 23. Nxe4 $16 Rc8 24. Bh3 Rc7 25. Be5 Nxe4 $1 26. Qxe4 ({Wrong is} 26. Bxc7 $2 Ng5 27. Bxd8 Nxf3+ 28. Kh1 Bxd8 $19) 26... Bd6 {[%cal Be7d6,Bd6e5,Be5c3][%mdl 32]} 27. Rxc4 Bxe5 28. Rxa4 Bc3 {Black is weak on the light squares} 29. Rc1 g6 30. Qf3 {[%cal Oh3f1] White is more active.} Qd2 31. Rd1 Qc2 32. Re4 Ra7 33. Qd3 Qxd3 {Weighted Error Value: White=0.09 (flawless) /Black=0.09 (flawless)} 1/2-1/2


