 (17... Nxe5 18. Bxf6 {Nice variation was after capture} Nxf3+ 19. gxf3 Bxh2+ 20. Kg2 Rh7 ({White would have strong initiative after} 20... O-O 21. Qh6) (20... Rg8 21. Re1+ Kf8 22. Qh6+) 21. Re1+ Kf8 22. Qg5 {Immediately losing was} Bd6 23. Re4 $1) 18. exf6 O-O-O 19. Bf4 Bd6 20. Bxd6 Qxd6 21. Rxa7 $3 {Second powerful strike!} Qxf6 22. Qa1 $1 Rhe8 23. Qa5 Qd6 24. Ra1 $1 Re7 25. Nd2 Rde8 26. Ne4 $1 {Every move improves position.} Qc7 27. Qb4 f5 28. Nd6+ $1 {Idea is practically the same.} Qxd6 29. Qxb7+ 1-0


