le Attack} 26. Rf1 Qxb3 27. Qxe7 Rfe8 28. Qd7 Qc4 29. Nc1 Rcd8 30. Qxa7 {[%eval -1121,23]} (30. Qc7 $142 {[%eval -515,21]} Rxd4 (30... Qxc7 $2 31. Bxc7 Rxd4 32. g3 $19) 31. Qxc4 Rxc4 32. h3) 30... Rxd4 {[%cal Oc4f1] ( -> ...Qxf1+!)} ({Weaker is} 30... Qxd4 31. Qxd4 Rxd4 32. f3 $17) 31. f4 Rd1 {[%csl Gc4][%cal Rd1f1]} 32. Qf2 Red8 33. Qe2 Rxf1+ {[%mdl 64] Remove Defender} 34. Kxf1 Rd1+ 35. Kf2 Qxe2+ 36. Kxe2 Rxc1 {[%mdl 4096] Endgame KR-KB} 37. Kd2 Rg1 38. Kxc2 Rxg2+ 39. Kd3 f5 40. Ke3 Kf7 41. Kf3 Ra2 42. Bf2 Ra4 {[%eval -605,26]} (42... Rxf2+ $142 {[%eval -1267,29]} 43. Kxf2 Ke6) 43. Be3 Kg6 44. h3 Kh5 45. Bf2 Ra3+ 46. Kg2 g5 {White must now prevent ...Ra2.} 47. fxg5 hxg5 {( -> ...Ra2)} 48. Bc5 Rb3 49. Bf2 Rb2 {Black mates.} 50. Kf3 {[#]} Rxf2+ $1 51. Kxf2 Kh4 52. Kg2 {Weighted Error Value: White=0.76/Black=0.39} f4 0-1


