{Ivanchuk ''Roiz,M: 'Rahal,Michael: 'Ivanchuk was trailing 2-1 at this point, so his only chance was to go all in to tie the match and try his luck with the tiebreaks.''' ' was trailing 2-1 at this point, so his only chance was to go all in to tie the match and try his luck with the tiebreaks. Roiz,M: 'Rahal,Michael: 'Ivanchuk was trailing 2-1 at this point, so his only chance was to go all in to tie the match and try his luck with the tiebreaks.''} 1. e4 {Roiz,M: 'Rahal,Michael: 'Roiz,M''} c5 2. Nf3 (2. Nc3 Nc6 3. Nge2 d6 4. d4 cxd4 5. Nxd4 {0-1 (54)'Roiz,M: '0-1 (54) Karthik,V (2519)-Maghsoodloo,P (2649) Manavgat 2018'' Karthik,V (2519)-Maghsoodloo,P (2649) Manavgat 2018 Roiz,M: '0-1 (54) Karthik,V (2519)-Maghsoodloo,P (2649) Manavgat 2018'}) 2... Nc6 (2... d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 {0-1 (41)'Roiz,M: '0-1 (41) Kuipers,S (2470)-Maghsoodloo,P (2679) Wijk aan Zee 2019'' Kuipers,S (2470)-Maghsoodloo,P (2679) Wijk aan Zee 2019 Roiz,M: '0-1 (41) Kuipers,S (2470)-Maghsoodloo,P (2679) Wijk aan Zee 2019'}) 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 d6 6. Bg5 {The Richt''Roiz,M: 'Rahal,Michael: 'The Richter-Rauzer attack against the Classical Sicilian. Although GM Kozul is the main man in the variation with Black, Maghsoodloo has played several games recently. However, I was slightly surprised to see that Ivanchuk had no recent games with White in this line.''' ' er-Rauzer attack against the Classical Sicilian. Although GM Kozul is the main man in the variation with Black, Maghsoodloo has played several games recently. However, I was slightly surprised to see that Ivanchuk had no recent games with White in this line. Roiz,M: 'Rahal,Michael: 'The Richter-Rauzer attack against the Classical Sicilian. Although GM Kozul is the main man in the variation with Black, Maghsoodloo has played several games recently. However, I was slightly surprised to see that Ivanchuk had no recent games with White in this line.''} e6 7. Qd2 (7. Bb5 Bd7 8. Qd3 h6 9. Bh4 Be7 10. O-O-O O-O 11. Bxc6 Bxc6 12